title: Diane Carey - STTNG 01 - Ghost Ship
description:
In 1995, a Russian aircraft carrier is destroyed by a mysterious creature that just as mysteriously disappears thereafter. Three hundred years later, Counselor Deanna Troi awakens in her quarters from a nightmare in which she senses the voices of the crew of that Russian ship, whose life-essences were somehow absorbed by the creature that destroyed them. And the nightmare heralds a danger to the Enterprise(TM) itself, for if Picard can't discover a way to communicate with the creature, it could absorb his crew just as it did the Russians.
